Class.ClassComment:
SetMapper /** * A set that maps another one to a new one of a possibly different type. Note this set is read only and doesn't accept write operations.

This class currently only accepts a {@link Function} that also implements {@link InjectiveFunction} so that it canguarantee the resulting mapped values are distinct from each other. This is important as many operations because very costly if this is not true.

Some operations such as {@link Collection#contains(Object)} and {@link Collection#containsAll(Collection)} may bemore expensive then normal since they cannot utilize lookups into the original collection. * @author wburns * @since 9.0 */
